Package it.unimi.dsi.fastutil.chars

Class AbstractChar2CharMap.BasicEntry

java.lang.Object
it.unimi.dsi.fastutil.chars.AbstractChar2CharMap.BasicEntry
All Implemented Interfaces:
Char2CharMap.Entry, Map.Entry<Character,Character>
Enclosing class:
AbstractChar2CharMap
public static class AbstractChar2CharMap.BasicEntry extends Object implements Char2CharMap.Entry
This class provides a basic but complete type-specific entry class for all those maps implementations that do not have entries on their own (e.g., most immutable maps).

This class does not implement setValue(), as the modification would not be reflected in the base map.
